<div class="content"><p>The <b>SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST</b> enumeration specifies if a
shadow of user input control is being requested.</p><dl>
<dd>
<div><pre> typedef  enum 
 {
   SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST_VIEW = 0,
   SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST_TAKECONTROL,
   SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST_Count
 } SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST;
</pre></div>
</dd></dl><p><b>SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST_VIEW:  </b>The shadow
request is for a view-only session. User input is not being requested.</p><p><b>SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST_TAKECONTROL:  </b>User
input control is being requested.</p><p><b>SHADOW_CONTROL_REQUEST_Count:  </b>Count of enum
values.</p></div>